body:
### Welcome 
Welcome to the GitHub Pages home of [Carl Woodhouse](http://www.cartlwoodhouse.com), a twenty something web developer from Sheffield, South Yorkshire .. that's in England. When not creating a virtual vision of the future on the internets i'm also a husband, dad, mountain bike enthusiast, lover of music, drinker of too much coffee and snow infatuatist. Here you'll find my musing on work, the virtues of life and just about everything in between ..
